olor: green;\">無須劣</span></span>!</strong><br />\n<br />\n應該揀邊隻? 唔駛我講喇啩! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0595e34c0477a7f776b54961dc47afede264bd8c","tid":486141,"uid":595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"九方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打慣單手打爽既，不過始終自己無學其他。公司電腦自己裝，但手機就唔方便"},{"pid":"f61304026aa1190df5213cc5dcf03fbaec04b8a5","tid":486141,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正所謂:<br />\n<strong>一日<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用九方</span></span>，終日<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心慌慌</span></span>!<br />\n一日<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">習倉頡</span></span>，以後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">無須劣</span></span>!</strong><br />\n<br />\n應該揀邊隻? 唔駛我講喇啩! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOnce with Q9, forever with しんぱい!<br />\nOnce learning Cang Jie, never having to inqui&egrave;ter!<br />\n<br />\nWhich choice? Needless to say!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e8a8de1163f07789df7a1b5c6274bfe31b663d","tid":486141,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T01:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己寫左個九方出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://avatar.hkepc.net/data/avatar/000/15/72/80_avatar_middle.jpg?random=1479561216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Favatar.hkepc.net%2Fdata%2Favatar%2F000%2F15%2F72%2F80_avatar_middle.jpg%3Frandom%3D1479561216&h=193dd473&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔用倉頡速成，linux都識用，冇理由區區速成會難到你</blockquote><br />\n因為自己整輸入法仲快<br />\nlinux係唔洗學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用嚟打機就要學</blockquote><br />\n師兄生活係咩時代，online game要打中文？"},{"pid":"32de8bfdcd9ebed4050cd08756e95bff01469849","tid":486141,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己寫左個九方出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://avatar.hkepc.net/data/avatar/000/15/72/80_avatar_middle.jpg?random=1479561216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Favatar.hkepc.net%2Fdata%2Favatar%2F000%2F15%2F72%2F80_avatar_middle.jpg%3Frandom%3D1479561216&h=193dd473&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔用倉頡速成，linux都識用，冇理由區區速成會難到你</blockquote><br />\n因為自己整輸入法仲快<br />\nlinux係唔洗學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用嚟打機就要學</blockquote><br />\n師兄生活係咩時代，online game要打中文？</blockquote><br />\n單論應用複雜性，<br />\n學用倉頡速成遠遠容易過喺linux寫script用kvm打機，<br />\n所以好奇怪點解咁複雜嘅嘢對你嚟講咁易上手，<br />\n叫你用倉頡速成反而就牙痛咁聲。"},{"pid":"99907a6aec75380cfc0de001f6a8ed673a85dcb6","tid":486141,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://avatar.hkepc.net/data/avatar/000/15/72/80_avatar_middle.jpg?random=1479561216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Favatar.hkepc.net%2Fdata%2Favatar%2F000%2F15%2F72%2F80_avatar_middle.jpg%3Frandom%3D1479561216&h=193dd473&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔用倉頡速成，linux都識用，冇理由區區速成會難到你</blockq