itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>初時比老闆笑，仲成日叫我學倉頡，但當佢睇完我打字個速度之後，佢就無再出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用九方都快過佢地用倉頡 劣幣驅良幣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明都已經有更方便快捷嘅輸入法，但唔知點解總係成爲唔倒主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4c803a9b219ce0634d5ce24b83b0a9af2e791b","tid":486141,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>初時比老闆笑，仲成日叫我學倉頡，但當佢睇完我打字個速度之後，佢就無再出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用九方都快過佢地用倉頡 劣幣驅良幣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明都已經有更方便快捷嘅輸入法，但唔知點解總係成爲唔倒主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為冇用"},{"pid":"144a6493f240d024e7f9ef509bbe50dd1ded3cc3","tid":486141,"uid":55523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"返左工後都係畫圖多，少打中文<br />\n又廢是係公司機裝九方（仲要自己俾錢買）<br />\n依家用chrome 個廣東話拼音就算，無用九方好耐了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b15c0af63f976bfbb1642ed62f2de04f7976f8","tid":486141,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T08:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>初時比老闆笑，仲成日叫我學倉頡，但當佢睇完我打字個速度之後，佢就無再出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用九方都快過佢地用倉頡 劣幣驅良幣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明都已經有更方便快捷嘅輸入法，但唔知點解總係成爲唔倒主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為冇用</blockquote><br />\n因為係商業軟件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反過嚟講，如果倉頡輸入法創始人朱先生，<br />\n仍然將其輸入法抱擁專利，果時本港嘅電腦中文輸入法，<br />\n可能係三強鼎立大競爭（倉頡、九方、縱橫）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11753d01336d77798dcd3302d2ea2086856158f","tid":486141,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"